column5: Yes buddy,I waded my way out at your old haunt. Just as the rain started,down went the float. Nothing like a Sunday morning quicky

Like I mentioned,the smoker was busy while I was away. Spoils of yesterdays catch. Dry brine for 6 hours, rinse,rack, let sit in the fridge til 4am this morning. Pop in the smoker with a pan of apple chunks,another added when I got home.
So you shipping that down to Chris UPS or Fedex??
Beauty fish. Looks like you got that smoker down pat !
jeez...clean as a whistle You ever get them on the fly?
Atta a boy, nice clean fish, no doubt it's tasty.
Sunday morning quicky I am hoping you just started.
When the water clears up and gets a bit colder, I will be tossing.
